ygData.messageBody:
Last Night, I handed in a box of kerra isle beetle
eyes and a mammoth tusk from everfrost and i completed
the quest. I get a message that i think might have to
do with your level so you can't get the next quest
until your a certain level or i jsut don't know
exactly what to say. I am gonna type out the paragraph
he says after i complete the quest and any suggestions
on what to say would be great! Here goes:

Excelent work young one. You are sure to be an asset
to our faction. Lets see if we can help you on your
journey to power.I believe this can be of assistance
to a young necromancer of [The Dead].

Well thats it...oh yeah and also the reward i got
forthe mammoth tusk and beetle eye quest was the level
22sk spell engulfing darkness so i think i did this
quest at the right time at least seeing as how i am
level 22. Well if anyone has any info or suggestions
that would be GREAT.

Tekman Hatebringer
Rodcet Nife
